Class SingleQuotaOfOffset

java.lang.Object
nusri.fyp.demo.entity.SingleQuotaOfOffset
All Implemented Interfaces:
SingleQuota
public class SingleQuotaOfOffset extends Object implements SingleQuota
Implementation of the SingleQuota interface for the "offset" mode quota entry.
Primarily includes the baseline value quota, upper/lower boundaries, and offset ratios.
